latestPosts.caption:
36 hour weekend getaway guide:
Delhi - Dehradun - Mussoorie - Landour - Delhi

Day 1: Leave Delhi at 6 a.m.
First Stop: Dehradoon Robbers Cave. Take your time exploring this place and have breakfast
Second Stop: Check in at your hotel in mussoorie, freshen up and leave for mall road. You can have Lunch at famous eateries like Kalsang or Chic Chocolate 
Third Stop: Head over to Lal Tibba view point in Landour to watch the sunset and have dinner at Landour Bakehouse / Rokeby Manor or Char Dukan
Day 2: Get up early and go for the George Everest Trek or Kempty Falls, have breakfast and head home!
